author: eTN Global Editor
title: Air India to launch nonstop Delhi-San Francisco service
text:
Air India to launch nonstop Delhi-San Francisco service     
NEW DELHI, India - Air India is to start nonstop Delhi San Francisco Delhi services from 2 December, 2015. This announcement was made by Indian Prime Minister, Mr. Narender Modi, during a visit to San Francisco, California last month. 
This will be the fourth gateway to USA, others being New York, Newark and Chicago.
